<bibRefCitation author="Zavala" box="[151,309,695,720]" pageId="32" pageNumber="433" refString="Bastida-Zavala, J. R. (2008) Serpulids (Annelida: Polychaeta) from the Eastern Pacific, including a brief mention of Hawaiian serpulids. Zootaxa, 1722, 1 - 61." type="journal article" year="2008">Zavala (2008)</bibRefCitation>
